data.title: rift quest:Highest of the Defiants
data.meta_description: Wiki article for rift quest:Highest of the Defiants :: Wiki
data.text:
This is one of the zone quests associated with Meridian: Ceremony of Attunement. This quest will only provide a reward the first time the instance is completed.

Follow Kaspar Massi to the Ceremony.

You'll meet him in front of the Catari Command Center and follow him inside.

Speak with Kaspar Massi.

Attend your ceremony.

Step into the Attunement Chamber.

This is the large machine that Sylver Valis powers up.

If this is your first time completing this instance, a tutorial window for Planar Attunement will pop up at the end of this step. You will gain two Planar Attunement levels.

Present your new self before the Defiants.
